docs.title: Welcome to the Breathe Model Docs
docs.text: Explore our documentation to get started using the Breathe Model library.

docs.title: Assemble Your First Model
docs.text:
Use the default model template to begin:

from breathe_model import Model
model = Model.from_default()

docs.title: Configure & Run
docs.text:
Configure the model and run it:

model.configure(input_voltage=3.7)
model.run()

docs.title: Install the Library
docs.text:
To get started with Breathe Model, install the library using:

pip install breathe-model

docs.title: Refresh & Verify
docs.text:
After installing, refresh your environment and verify:

breathe-model --version
